we have released Proxmox WHMCS module version 1.3.1 today with the following new features:

 •  VM Templates: KVM Template, kvm Auto OS install using Clone/Template .&lt;br /&gt;
 •  Client Area: Ability to change openvz password using the Change Password option in WHMC (require ssh2 setup).&lt;br /&gt;
 •  VM Management: Ability to migrate VM.&lt;br /&gt;

